note:
Wildman, Bryce Terry is an out & proud entertainer who has made it his goal to carry on the retro sound of glam rock. With an impressive resume of many years of working in all different aspects of show-business, it is no question that Bryce knows how to put on a show and give an entertaining performance.
 
“I just want people to dance, sing along and just have an amazing time.”-BT
 
He made his debut into the music world with his first single, Wildman which debuted on New Years Eve in 2022.
